Maher, Respondent, v. Willson, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. May 27, 1889.) Action by Dennis Maher against Mrs. George W. Willson. See 3 H. Y. Supp. 80.

Argued before Learned, P. J., and Landon and Ingalls, JJ.

Ho opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and printing disbursements.
